                        <item xml:id="e1">- The title ግዕዙና። ረዕየ።[sic] ዮሐንስ። is written on the front
                           board with yellow modern paint. 
 - Names are written in the margins
                           of Text XXIII each referring (with a sign in the shape of a cross) to one
                           of the angels of the seven assemblies, in a secondary hand: Yoḥannǝs
                              (<locus target="#183ra">183ra</locus>), Herenewos (<locus target="#183va">183va</locus>), Gayǝyos (<locus target="#183vb">183vb</locus>), ʾAṭṭiqos (<locus target="#184ra">184ra</locus>),
