               <provenance>In Additio 3, the name of the original
                     commissioner has been erased. According to Additio 4, Walda Gabrǝʾel (and his
                     wife Walatta Māryām) at some point donated the Ms. to Kidāna Mǝḥrat May
                     ʾAnbäsa.</provenance></history>
